WEBVTT

1
00:14:51.491 --> 00:14:53.163 
这很尴尬。
THIS IS AWKWARD.

2
00:14:53.163 --> 00:14:55.165 
我们没有点意大利香肠。
WE DIDN'T ORDER PEPPERONI.

3
00:14:58.168 --> 00:15:00.330 
我的生活是一场灾难，泰迪。
MY LIFE IS A DISASTER, TEDDY.

4
00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:02.172 
都是你的错。
AND IT'S ALL YOUR FAULT.

5
00:15:02.172 --> 00:15:03.903 
故障故障。。。
FAULT FAULT...

6
00:15:03.903 --> 00:15:05.035 
你在做什么？
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

7
00:15:06.076 --> 00:15:08.108 
我以为梦结束了。
I THOUGHT THE DREAM WAS OVER.

8
00:15:08.108 --> 00:15:11.581 
不，我得说当梦想结束的时候。。。
NO. I GET TO SAY WHEN THE DREAM IS OVER...

9
00:15:11.581 --> 00:15:14.584 
（回声）完毕。。。
( echoing ) OVER OVER OVER...

10
00:15:15.685 --> 00:15:17.217 
（喘息）
( gasps )

